{
  "title": "No Helmet",
  "body": [
    "In Colorado,",
    "I saw someone",
    "crash their bike",
    "and lose the dignity",
    "of an old man.",
    "He didn't want help.",
    "But when people care,",
    "they help.",
    "And he wasn't wearing a helmet.",
    "But when people love you,",
    "they make you wear helmets.",
    "So I don't know if he truly lived",
    "with any room",
    "for that sort of thing."
  ],
  "date": "5/14/2026"
}